title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“When multiplying a newton by a meter, for example, MicroMath automatically displays the result in jewels.” [From MacWeek, 3 February 1992, p. 17. Submitted by Tony Waters, Catonville, Maryland.]
